query:
SELECT
            slot,
            beacon_validators_balance.gwei AS beacon_balances,
            beacon_blocks.deposit_sum_aggregated AS beacon_deposits,
            beacon_blocks.block_hash,
            execution_supply.balances_sum::TEXT AS execution_balances,
            timestamp AS beacon_timestamp
        FROM
            beacon_states
        JOIN beacon_blocks ON beacon_blocks.state_root = beacon_states.state_root
        JOIN beacon_validators_balance ON beacon_validators_balance.state_root = beacon_states.state_root
        JOIN execution_supply ON execution_supply.block_hash = beacon_blocks.block_hash
        ORDER BY slot DESC
